Seafoodjackie</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2hIHbgy</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MadJuansReturn]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Rest in peace to Brenda Fricker, AKA “Pigeon Lady.”</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/GknDtiG</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dtGj3mE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/GknDtiG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[rabbihimself]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Self-WARGLARGAHARBL Toy</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wr2Oues</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZBbFH03.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wr2Oues</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LogicDude]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fucking Funny How "Judicial Independence" Gets Really Flexible Around Billionaires</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/jsoDPtt</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rEcsn34.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jrHMWsB.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>One of the strangest fucking debates in modern politics is whether Supreme Court justices should accept lavish gifts from billionaires.
Imagine explaining that sentence to someone in 1990.
"Wait... that's... legal?" 

Judges are supposed to be independent.
Not sponsored.
If your highest court starts looking like an influencer posting "Thanks to my generous benefactors!" we've wandered into a parody of democracy. ⚖️

Notice how every proposal for stronger ethics rules is treated as some outrageous assault on the judiciary.
No, Karen.
The assault is creating a system where public trust depends on hoping nobody's yacht invitation influences anything. 

The rule shouldn't be controversial.
Justice shouldn't come with complimentary vacations, luxury hospitality, or billionaire perks.
If people lose faith that the referee is impartial, eventually they stop believing in the fucking game. ⚖️

